# C9 (Tier2H): un-ignore docs/archive so the superseded Task F design docs are
# tracked — a gitignored archive is not memory. Keep other archive contents ignored.
!docs/archive/
docs/archive/*
!docs/archive/Tier1_TaskF_spatial_resampling_spec_v2.md
!docs/archive/Gayini_subsampling_approach.md
R/obs/

# Script history is now tracked through docs/scripts_manifest.csv
# and scripts/archive/ manifests. Do not add a new scripts/obs/
# compatibility folder; archive legacy scripts under scripts/archive/.

